{"tid":2476994,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"丁權 佢又講得幾岩","createTime":"2021-04-06T02:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:38:38.000Z","uid":101341,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"151e37393a78feca4b320cc11bbbc23a2933f77f","tid":2476994,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7JtWFt_G5NA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7JtWFt_G5NA&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1a527efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7JtWFt_G5NA</a><br />\n<br />\n塊地原本係我，你地冇地關我撚事，憑咩管我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7970e2e94faa2a88f956ac73c546e62e70baa89","tid":2476994,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"其實佢又唔exactly錯得晒<br />\n<br />\n規劃呢樣野係好現代嘅concept。政府同你講你塊地淨係可以起乜先可以起乜，但明明塊地係自己嘅，點解可以咁樣受人規管？<br />\n<br />\n學佢話齋，新界唔淨係得原居民，亦有男有女。所以，根據佢講法，丁權係應該取消，人人都可以起。<br />\n<br />\n之但係，學佢咁樣「放任式」取消丁權又唔多work，因為現實上，起樓係需要基建support，路、渠、鐵路、社區設施等等等，而基建嘅錢應該係源自地價/補地價。<br />\n<br />\n呢種「放任式」起樓，同現代嘅規劃模式唔多夾。"},{"pid":"be6f38cfa070266d8eac638d339e3a0885d06f86","tid":2476994,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"好呀，要繼續加油，等睇成為condom"},{"pid":"bc2d7d59664b84af84ac9d7aecfea19b64f200e4","tid":2476994,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T05:43:01.000Z","msg":"出鄉黑有佢一套歪理<br />\n佢係高級"},{"pid":"4893f7b9e5583dd6f876659b9d53f40880c78fd9","tid":2476994,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"留返同黨講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97ff40fd9995742d587ce24af291614812f60df","tid":2476994,"uid":260744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"塊地係黨，候強已犯國安法"},{"pid":"883e06ccfc40fa6515b7774be5447224cd243e14","tid":2476994,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"151e37393a78feca4b320cc11bbbc23a2933f77f","tid":2476994,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7JtWFt_G5NA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7JtWFt_G5NA&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1a527efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7JtWFt_G5NA</a><br />\n<br />\n塊地原本係我，你地冇地關我撚事，憑咩管我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"憑我實力。。。。"},{"pid":"1c9394024bd246c1a28289ae318ea2640e76781d","tid":2476994,"uid":56424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"On Lun 99<br />\n<br />\n而家嘈緊嗰啲全撚部都係生人霸死地<br />\n<br />\n你真係伯爺有張清朝張契英撚時代登記左就係任你起，冇嘅話你講經咩"},{"pid":"47bc41849b117190b4f1c8a59bd19269badcdaae","tid":2476994,"uid":56424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:05:59.000Z","msg":"香港的原居民歷史是由1840年鴉片戰爭爆發時，英軍佔領香港島原居民的土地開始，由於清廷欽差大臣琦善與英國政府草擬《穿鼻草約》時，由於清廷及英國政經界分別認為有辱國體及獲利太少，故雙方不承認《穿鼻草約》的存在，但英國軍隊並沒有撤出香港島。1842年《南京條約》簽訂，香港割讓予英國之後，香港政府便要求香港島土地的地主（通常是居住於新界的原居民）以中國地契換為港英政府地契，很多地主都沒有換契，於是香港政府便沒收這些華人原居民的土地，並拍賣成為香港政府的收入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/新界原居民\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=f0ee1014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/新界原居民</a><br />\n<br />\n你有契換點起都得"},{"pid":"d2ac29df2633a425cfed92af65c37f833a1f3a9c","tid":2476994,"uid":56424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cheungchaumagazine.com/長洲雜誌/tag/land-title-土地業權/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cheungchaumagazine.com%2F%E9%95%B7%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C%2Ftag%2Fland-title-%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E6%A5%AD%E6%AC%8A%2F&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7684e9b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cheungchaumagazine.com/長洲雜誌/tag/land-title-土地業權/</a><br />\n<br />\n點解地皮叫地皮？<br />\n<br />\n冇紅契丁乜權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43314847c347fc769a4c29ecff3a2a2c6155397f","tid":2476994,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"無地無丁既繼續打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}